@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to MiniClinic</h1>
    <p>
        MiniClinic is a comprehensive healthcare management solution built with ASP.NET Core. This application is designed to streamline patient care and medical record management.
    </p>
    <p>
        <strong>For Admins:</strong> Admins have full control over user creation. They can create new doctor accounts as well as patient profiles.
        When creating a patient, a doctor must be assigned immediately to ensure proper care coordination.
    </p>
    <p>
        <strong>For Doctors:</strong> Doctors can view the list of their assigned patients, access detailed medical records, and create new medical records as needed.
    </p>
    <p>
        All data displayed in the app is retrieved from a robust external API and securely stored in the local database.
    </p>
    <p>
        Learn more about <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/aspnet/core">building Web apps with ASP.NET Core</a>.
    </p>
</div>
